data.description: Introducing a charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom rambler nestled within a picturesque lake community. This single-story home offers a seamless blend of comfort and convenience, perfect for those seeking a tranquil lakeside lifestyle. Step inside to discover an inviting floor plan, allowing for effortless movement between the living, dining, and kitchen areas. Outside, embrace the beauty of nature with a large semi-wooded lot, ideal for outdoor activities and gatherings. As part of the lake community, residents can enjoy exclusive access to the shimmering waters, whether it's for boating, fishing, or simply taking in the breathtaking views. With its desirable location and the allure of lakeside living, this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom rambler presents an exceptional opportunity to embrace a serene and fulfilling lifestyle. Back on the market no fault to seller, buyer financing fell through. Property being sold as is.
